title: Dakine Pyro Kite Harness
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Pyro Kite Harness in Rasta.

Harness Features:
- Power Clip Lock buckle system
- Hammerhead spreader bar
- Spreader bar pad
- Dual blade hook knife
- Pre-curved P.E.B inner support structure
- Featherweight ES foam molded
